title: Tumi Arrive Owen Crossbody 255030 - Overview
description:
Tumi Arrive Owen Crossbody - 255030-PEWTER
http://www.abt.com/product/96565/Tumi-255030PEWTER.html?utm_source=youtube&utm_medium=video&utm_campaign=255030_20160506

TUMI presents the relaunch of its Arrivé collection. Meticulously appointed with the finest aesthetic and engineering features this versatile crossbody silhouette has an adjustable shoulder strap quick-access pockets for small essentials and can even accommodate your iPad. Take it anywhere and everywhere.
Features:
• Primary Material: Fabric 
• Interior Features:
o Zip pocket with TUMI ID Lock™ protective lining
o iPad pocket
o Hook with leather strap (key ring can be attached by snap closure)
• Exterior Features:
o Zip entry to main compartment
o Silver piping detail on front zip pocket
o Front zip pocket
o Quick-access protective front pocket with hidden magnetic closure
